short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Developer Tool to analyze Svelte apps and list component trees, state, and render timing

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sveltime is a Chrome DevTools extension for developers actively building their website using the Svelte framework.  Sveltime will show the component tree as it is currently being rendered.  Each component will also have the option to see what state is currently associated with it.  The render time will also be displayed for each component.
